    <section id="sect-00001">
      <title/>
      <para id="para-00001">Drug conversion tables are utilized with dosage calculations to ensure an appropriate dosage of a drug is being administered to the client as ordered.</para>
      <para id="para-00001a"><link target-id="table-00001" document="m00381"/> shows common metric and U.S. customary units of measurement used in health <link target-id="table-00002" document="m00381"/> shows household equivalents.</para>
